---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Portfolio
description: "A selection of Reimund Schlosser's work across strategic HR — business partnering, org design, culture, and rewards."
css:
  - /css/portfolio.css
---
<div class="page-head">
  <div class="cell a"></div><div class="cell b"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>My <span class="glow">Portfolio</span></h1>
    <p class="intro">A selection of my work across strategic HR — from business partnering and org design to culture, rewards, and everything that makes global teams thrive. Each project tells the story of a challenge, a solution, and the people it helped.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="grid-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="p-grid">
      {%- for project in collections.portfolio %}
      <a class="tile" href="{{ project.url }}">
        <div class="ph{% if not project.data.tileImage %} g{{ project.data.order }}{% endif %}"{% if project.data.tileImage %} style="background-image:url('{{ project.data.tileImage }}')"{% endif %}>
          {%- if not project.data.tileImage %}<span class="num">{{ "0" if project.data.order < 10 else "" }}{{ project.data.order }}</span>{%- endif %}
        </div>
        <h3>{{ project.data.title }}</h3>
        <span class="more">View project →</span>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
